{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1166,"text":"I've been living in rural East Africa\nfor about 10 years,"},{"time":4260,"text":"and I want to share a field perspective\nwith you on global poverty."},{"time":7934,"text":"I believe that the greatest failure\nof the human race"},{"time":10532,"text":"is the fact that we've left more than\none billion of our members behind."},{"time":14335,"text":"Hungry, extreme poverty:"},{"time":16701,"text":"these often seem like gigantic,\ninsurmountable problems,"},{"time":20013,"text":"too big to solve."},{"time":22006,"text":"But as a field practitioner,"},{"time":23739,"text":"I believe these are actually\nvery solvable problems"},{"time":26567,"text":"if we just take the right strategies."}]},{"cues":[{"time":30390,"text":"Archimedes was an ancient Greek thinker,"},{"time":32529,"text":"and he taught us that if we lean\non the right levers,"},{"time":35037,"text":"we can move the world."},{"time":36959,"text":"In the fight against extreme poverty,\nI believe there are three powerful levers"},{"time":40699,"text":"that we can lean on."},{"time":42096,"text":"This talk is all about those levers,\nand why they make poverty"},{"time":45122,"text":"a winnable fight in our lifetimes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":47994,"text":"What is extreme poverty?"},{"time":50287,"text":"When I first moved to rural East Africa,"},{"time":52256,"text":"I stayed overnight with a farm family."},{"time":54629,"text":"They were wonderful people."},{"time":56753,"text":"They invited me into their home.\nWe sang songs together"},{"time":59649,"text":"and ate a simple dinner."},{"time":60824,"text":"They gave me a blanket\nto sleep on the floor."},{"time":63359,"text":"In the morning, however,\nthere was nothing to eat."},{"time":66265,"text":"And then at lunchtime, I watched\nwith an increasingly sick feeling"},{"time":70041,"text":"as the eldest girl in the family\ncooked porridge as a substitute for lunch."},{"time":74703,"text":"For that meal, every child\ndrank one cup to survive."},{"time":79575,"text":"And I cannot tell you how ashamed I felt"},{"time":81589,"text":"when they handed one of those cups to me,"},{"time":83576,"text":"and I knew I had to accept\ntheir hospitality."}]},{"cues":[{"time":86781,"text":"Children need food not only to survive\nbut also to grow physically and mentally."},{"time":91265,"text":"Every day they fail to eat,\nthey lose a little bit of their future."},{"time":95114,"text":"Amongst the extreme poor,\none in three children"},{"time":98020,"text":"are permanently stunted\nfrom a lifetime of not eating enough."},{"time":102326,"text":"When that's combined\nwith poor access to health care,"},{"time":104862,"text":"one in 10 extremely poor children\ndie before they reach age five."},{"time":109819,"text":"And only one quarter of children\ncomplete high school"},{"time":112380,"text":"because they lack school fees."},{"time":113908,"text":"Hunger and extreme poverty curb\nhuman potential in every possible way."},{"time":120771,"text":"We see ourselves as a thinking,\nfeeling and moral human race,"},{"time":125085,"text":"but until we solve these problems\nfor all of our members,"},{"time":128144,"text":"we fail that standard,"},{"time":130332,"text":"because every person\non this planet matters."},{"time":132698,"text":"This child matters."},{"time":135125,"text":"These children matter."},{"time":137638,"text":"This girl matters."}]},{"cues":[{"time":140209,"text":"You know, we see things like this,"},{"time":141922,"text":"and we're upset by them,"},{"time":143523,"text":"but they seem like such big problems."},{"time":145349,"text":"We don't know how\nto take effective action."},{"time":148893,"text":"But remember our friend Archimedes."},{"time":151572,"text":"Global poverty has powerful levers."},{"time":153924,"text":"It's a problem like any other."},{"time":156023,"text":"I live and work in the field,\nand as a practitioner,"},{"time":158493,"text":"I believe these are very\nsolvable problems."},{"time":161320,"text":"So for the next 10 minutes,"},{"time":162825,"text":"let's not be sad\nabout the state of the world."},{"time":165003,"text":"Let's engage our brains."},{"time":166858,"text":"Let's engage our collective passion\nfor problem-solving"},{"time":169627,"text":"and figure out what those levers are."}]},{"cues":[{"time":172416,"text":"Lever number one: most\nof the world's poor are farmers."},{"time":176157,"text":"Think about how extraordinary this is."},{"time":178244,"text":"If this picture represents\nthe world's poor,"},{"time":180729,"text":"then more than half engage in farming\nas a major source of income."},{"time":184368,"text":"This gets me really excited."},{"time":186319,"text":"All of these people, one profession."},{"time":189247,"text":"Think how powerful this is."},{"time":190727,"text":"When farmers become more productive,\nthen more than half the world's poor"},{"time":194269,"text":"earn more money and climb out of poverty."},{"time":196697,"text":"And it gets better."},{"time":197941,"text":"The product of farming\nis, of course, food."},{"time":200220,"text":"So when farmers become more productive,\nthey earn more food,"},{"time":203849,"text":"and they don't just help themselves,"},{"time":205594,"text":"but they help to feed healthy communities\nand thriving economies."},{"time":209228,"text":"And when farmers become more productive,\nthey reduce environmental pressure."},{"time":213443,"text":"We only have two ways\nwe can feed the world:"},{"time":215749,"text":"we can either make our existing farmland\na lot more productive,"},{"time":219096,"text":"or we can clear cut forest and savannah\nto make more farmland,"},{"time":222400,"text":"which would be environmentally disastrous."},{"time":225688,"text":"Farmers are basically\na really important leverage point."},{"time":229496,"text":"When farmers become more productive,"},{"time":231453,"text":"they earn more income,\nthey climb out of poverty,"},{"time":234088,"text":"they feed their communities and they\nreduce environmental land pressure."},{"time":238187,"text":"Farmers stand at the center of the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":242306,"text":"And not a farmer like this one,"},{"time":244030,"text":"but rather this lady."},{"time":246055,"text":"Most of the farmers I know\nare actually women."},{"time":248699,"text":"Look at the strength and the will\nradiating from this woman."},{"time":251995,"text":"She is physically strong, mentally tough,"},{"time":254231,"text":"and she will do whatever it takes\nto earn a better life for her children."},{"time":257686,"text":"If we're going to put the future\nof humanity in one person's hands,"},{"time":260854,"text":"then I'm really glad it's her."}]},{"cues":[{"time":262691,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":268125,"text":"There's just one problem:"},{"time":269405,"text":"many smallholder farmers\nlack access to basic tools and knowledge."},{"time":274748,"text":"Currently, they take a little bit\nof saved food grain from the prior year,"},{"time":278460,"text":"they plant it in the ground\nand they till it with a manual hand hoe."},{"time":281864,"text":"These are tools and techniques\nthat date to the Bronze Age,"},{"time":284653,"text":"and it's why many farmers\nare still very poor."}]},{"cues":[{"time":288755,"text":"But good news, again."},{"time":290161,"text":"Lever number two:"},{"time":291336,"text":"humanity actually solved the problem\nof agricultural poverty a century ago."},{"time":296449,"text":"Let me walk you through the three\nmost basic factors in farming."},{"time":299944,"text":"First, hybrid seed is created\nwhen you cross two seeds together."},{"time":304365,"text":"If you naturally pollinate\na high-yielding variety"},{"time":307193,"text":"together with a drought-resistant variety,"},{"time":309528,"text":"you get a hybrid that inherits\npositive traits from both of its parents."},{"time":313390,"text":"Next, conventional fertilizer,\nif used responsibly,"},{"time":317111,"text":"is environmentally sustainable."},{"time":319433,"text":"If you micro-dose\njust a pinch of fertilizer"},{"time":322451,"text":"to a plant that's taller than I am,"},{"time":324559,"text":"you unlock enormous yield gain."},{"time":327118,"text":"These are known as farm inputs."},{"time":329241,"text":"Farm inputs need to be combined\nwith good practice."},{"time":331865,"text":"When you space your seeds\nand plant with massive amounts of compost,"},{"time":335983,"text":"farmers multiply their harvests."},{"time":338946,"text":"These proven tools and practices\nhave more than tripled"},{"time":341546,"text":"agricultural productivity\nin every major region of the world,"},{"time":344618,"text":"moving mass numbers of people\nout of poverty."},{"time":347928,"text":"We just haven't finished delivering\nthese things to everybody just yet,"},{"time":351291,"text":"particularly in Sub-Saharan Africa."}]},{"cues":[{"time":353925,"text":"So overall, this is amazing news."},{"time":355671,"text":"Humanity actually solved\nagricultural poverty a century ago,"},{"time":359677,"text":"in theory."},{"time":360908,"text":"We just haven't delivered these things\nto everybody just yet."},{"time":364354,"text":"In this century, the reason\nthat people remain poor"},{"time":366765,"text":"is because maybe they live\nin remote places."},{"time":368995,"text":"They lack access to these things."},{"time":372154,"text":"Therefore, ending poverty\nis simply a matter"},{"time":374739,"text":"of delivering proven goods\nand services to people."},{"time":378185,"text":"We don't need more genius types right now."},{"time":380507,"text":"The humble delivery guy is going\nto end global poverty in our lifetime."}]},{"cues":[{"time":386088,"text":"So these are the three levers,"},{"time":387600,"text":"and the most powerful lever\nis simply delivery."},{"time":391033,"text":"Wherever the world's companies,\ngovernments and nonprofits"},{"time":394344,"text":"set up delivery networks\nfor life-improving goods,"},{"time":397400,"text":"we eliminate poverty."}]},{"cues":[{"time":400023,"text":"OK, so that sounds really nice in theory,"},{"time":402040,"text":"but what about in practice?"},{"time":403354,"text":"What do these delivery networks look like?"},{"time":406006,"text":"I want to share the concrete example\nthat I know best,"},{"time":408565,"text":"my organization, One Acre Fund."},{"time":411165,"text":"We only serve the farmer,"},{"time":412584,"text":"and our job is to provide her\nwith the tools that she needs to succeed."},{"time":416284,"text":"We start off by delivering farm inputs\nto really rural places."},{"time":419262,"text":"Now, this may appear\ninitially very challenging,"},{"time":421552,"text":"but it's pretty possible. Let me show you."},{"time":423787,"text":"We buy farm inputs with the combined power\nof our farmer network,"},{"time":426871,"text":"and store it in 20 warehouses like this."},{"time":429638,"text":"Then, during input delivery,\nwe rent hundreds of 10-ton trucks"},{"time":433638,"text":"and send them out to where farmers\nare waiting in the field."},{"time":436953,"text":"They then get their individual orders\nand walk it home to their farms."},{"time":440415,"text":"It's kind of like Amazon\nfor rural farmers."},{"time":443694,"text":"Importantly, realistic delivery\nalso includes finance, a way to pay."},{"time":448536,"text":"Farmers pay us little by little over time,\ncovering most of our expenses."},{"time":453587,"text":"And then we surround\nall that with training."},{"time":456151,"text":"Our rural field officers\ndeliver practical, hands-on training"},{"time":459826,"text":"to farmers in the field"},{"time":461255,"text":"every two weeks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":463496,"text":"Wherever we deliver our services,\nfarmers use these tools"},{"time":467104,"text":"to climb out of poverty."},{"time":469193,"text":"This is a farmer\nin our program, Consolata."},{"time":472033,"text":"Look at the pride on her face."},{"time":474212,"text":"She has achieved a modest prosperity\nthat I believe is the human right"},{"time":477894,"text":"of every hardworking person on the planet."},{"time":481264,"text":"Today, I'm proud to say that we're serving\nabout 400,000 farmers like Consolata."}]},{"cues":[{"time":486190,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":491881,"text":"The key to doing this\nis scalable delivery."},{"time":494482,"text":"In any given area, we hire\na rural field officer"},{"time":497395,"text":"who delivers our services\nto 200 farmers, on average,"},{"time":500575,"text":"with more than 1,000 people\nliving in those families."},{"time":503805,"text":"Today, we have 2,000\nof these rural field officers"},{"time":507260,"text":"growing very quickly."},{"time":508665,"text":"This is our delivery army,"},{"time":510991,"text":"and we're just one organization."},{"time":512682,"text":"There are many companies,\ngovernments and nonprofits"},{"time":515870,"text":"that have delivery armies just like this."},{"time":518105,"text":"And I believe we stand at a moment in time"},{"time":520175,"text":"where collectively, we are capable of\ndelivering farm services to all farmers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":525755,"text":"Let me show you how possible this is."},{"time":527960,"text":"This is a map of Sub-Saharan Africa,"},{"time":529853,"text":"with a map of the United States for scale."},{"time":531982,"text":"I chose Sub-Saharan Africa because\nthis is a huge delivery territory."},{"time":535394,"text":"It's very challenging."},{"time":537248,"text":"But we analyzed every 50-mile\nby 50-mile block on the continent,"},{"time":541292,"text":"and we found that half of farmers\nlive in just these shaded regions."},{"time":547265,"text":"That's a remarkably small area overall."},{"time":550195,"text":"If you were to lay these boxes\nnext to each other"},{"time":552528,"text":"within a map of the United States,"},{"time":554188,"text":"they would only cover\nthe Eastern United States."},{"time":557284,"text":"You can order pizza\nanywhere in this territory"},{"time":560832,"text":"and it'll arrive to your house\nhot, fresh and delicious."},{"time":564581,"text":"If America can deliver pizza\nto an area of this size,"},{"time":567872,"text":"then Africa's companies,\ngovernments and non-profits"},{"time":570919,"text":"can deliver farm services\nto all of her farmers."},{"time":573966,"text":"This is possible."}]},{"cues":[{"time":576995,"text":"I'm going to wrap up by generalizing\nbeyond just farming."},{"time":580292,"text":"In every field of human development,"},{"time":582423,"text":"humanity has already invented\neffective tools to end poverty."},{"time":586276,"text":"We just need to deliver them."},{"time":588322,"text":"So again, in every area\nof human development,"},{"time":590587,"text":"super-smart people a long time ago\ninvented inexpensive,"},{"time":594013,"text":"highly effective tools."},{"time":595869,"text":"Humanity is armed to the teeth"},{"time":597825,"text":"with simple, effective\nsolutions to poverty."},{"time":601596,"text":"We just need to deliver these\nto a pretty small area."},{"time":605266,"text":"Again using the map\nof Sub-Saharan Africa as an example,"},{"time":608392,"text":"remember that rural poverty is\nconcentrated in these blue shaded areas."},{"time":612440,"text":"Urban poverty is even more concentrated,\nin these green little dots."},{"time":617282,"text":"Again, using a map\nof the United States for scale,"},{"time":620317,"text":"this is what I would call\na highly achievable delivery zone."},{"time":624346,"text":"In fact, for the first time\nin human history,"},{"time":626532,"text":"we have a vast amount of delivery\ninfrastructure available to us."},{"time":630055,"text":"The world's companies,\ngovernments and non-profits"},{"time":632803,"text":"have delivery armies\nthat are fully capable"},{"time":635050,"text":"of covering this relatively small area."},{"time":637927,"text":"We just lack the will."}]},{"cues":[{"time":640913,"text":"If we are willing,"},{"time":642348,"text":"every one of us has a role to play."},{"time":645920,"text":"We first need more people to pursue\ncareers in human development,"},{"time":649315,"text":"especially if you live\nin a developing nation."},{"time":651487,"text":"We need more front line health workers,\nteachers, farmer trainers,"},{"time":654997,"text":"sales agents for life-improving goods."},{"time":657439,"text":"These are the delivery people\nthat dedicate their careers"},{"time":660133,"text":"to improving the lives of others."},{"time":662532,"text":"But we also need a lot of support roles."},{"time":665731,"text":"These are roles available\nat just my organization alone,"},{"time":668606,"text":"and we're just one out of many."},{"time":670399,"text":"This may surprise you, but no matter\nwhat your technical specialty,"},{"time":674197,"text":"there is a role for you in this fight."},{"time":677158,"text":"And no matter how logistically possible\nit is to end poverty,"},{"time":680529,"text":"we need a lot more resources."},{"time":682448,"text":"This is our number one constraint."},{"time":684811,"text":"For private investors, we need\na big expansion of venture capital,"},{"time":688211,"text":"private equity, working capital,\navailable in emerging markets."},{"time":692477,"text":"But there are also limits\nto what private business can accomplish."},{"time":695928,"text":"Private businesses often struggle\nto profitably serve the extreme poor,"},{"time":699897,"text":"so philanthropy still has\na major role to play."},{"time":702998,"text":"Anybody can give,\nbut we need more leadership."},{"time":706112,"text":"We need more visionary philanthropists"},{"time":708083,"text":"and global leaders who will take\nproblems in human development"},{"time":712019,"text":"and lead humanity to wipe them\noff the face of the planet."},{"time":716276,"text":"If you're interested in these ideas,\ncheck out this website."}]},{"cues":[{"time":719122,"text":"We need more leaders."},{"time":722174,"text":"Humanity has put people on the moon."},{"time":724220,"text":"We've invented supercomputers\nthat fit into our pockets"},{"time":726821,"text":"and connect us with anybody on the planet."},{"time":728901,"text":"We've run marathons\nat a five-minute mile pace."},{"time":732207,"text":"We are an exceptional people."},{"time":735822,"text":"But we've left more than one billion\nof our members behind."},{"time":739485,"text":"Until every girl like this one\nhas an opportunity"},{"time":741807,"text":"to earn her full human potential,"},{"time":744047,"text":"we have failed to become\na truly moral and just human race."},{"time":748516,"text":"Logistically speaking,\nit's incredibly possible"},{"time":751296,"text":"to end extreme poverty."},{"time":753220,"text":"We just need to deliver\nproven goods and services"},{"time":756126,"text":"to everybody."},{"time":757665,"text":"If we have the will, every one of us\nhas a role to play."},{"time":762024,"text":"Let's deploy our time, our careers,"},{"time":764937,"text":"our collective wealth."},{"time":766781,"text":"Let us deliver an end to extreme poverty"},{"time":769541,"text":"in this lifetime."}]},{"cues":[{"time":771971,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":773146,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}